Description: Utilities for exporting exercises from 'R/exams' to
    question pools for the learning management system 'ILIAS'. The
    package provides an 'ILIAS'-specific QTI 1.2 rendering path and
    writes the question-pool XML layout validated for imports in
    'ILIAS' 9.17. Supported exercise types include cloze, single-choice,
    multiple-choice, numeric, and string questions.
